citations.desc: Access and inspection of records and property; submission of itineraries.
citations.narrative:
A responsible adult was not available to accompany APHIS Officials during the inspection process at 10:45am on 01-
June-2023.
The inspectors arrived at the facility at 10:45am and made contact with a facility employee whom stated to call the
licensee or facility representative. The inspectors called the licensee and facility representative and left messages. The
facility representative called back and stated an authorized person was not able to do an inspection today. The inspectors
then left the facility.
Additional Inspectors:
William Janecke, VETERINARY MEDICAL OFFICEREnd Section
